label: aluminum ion

label: antimony-121 atom
editors note: CHEBI:30304 is the only case (so far) where antimony(0), in the elemental antimony hierarchy is also superclass to the atom terms (antimony-121/3 atom).

label: copper-63 atom
editors note: Note for copper CHEBI has copper-63 as subclass to copper(O) under elemental copper not subclass to copper atom, this pattern makes sense but is different then other CHEBI terms FIX.
